  "text": "Another point to be noted is that owing to the indirect optimization of the polynomial coefficients, there were certain junctures when the planned trajectories dramatically veered. This effect was starkly visible especially when the nonlinear model predictive controller [CITATION_1] was used for tracking trajectories. These dramatic changes were akin to an exaggerated version of random restarts used in local trajectory planning [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
